channel.title: How do i add full vesta and statius to delta
channel.description: Well im pretty new to rsps coding i know the basics but i just don't know how to add full vesta and statius to my server can someone please help and post models if you can :) thanks.

item.title: How do i add full vesta and statius to delta
item.dc:creator: @xthekingx xthekingx
item.description:
@xthekingx wrote:

[quote=“jailed, post:2, topic:358619”]find the a pvp model set here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/board,129.0.html
and download the models + ints and paste the models into the “models” folder in your client.
then paste the ints in “class8.java” in your client.
then save, compile and run server then when you log in type “add model modelnumber”
to all the models you added in the “model” folder.
then you have added the pvp armour. just spawn the id’s in the ints.[/quote]

when i type “add model #” it says unable to find the model
